query: SELECT a.id as account_id, a.name as account_name, a.plan_key, a.status as account_status, s.id as sub_id, s.plan_id, s.status as sub_status, s.billing_cycle, p.name as plan_name, p.plan_key as plan_key_from_plan FROM accounts a LEFT JOIN subscriptions s ON s.account_id = a.id LEFT JOIN plans p ON p.id = s.plan_id;
